description:
MrBeast is building a Big Game campaign in just 27 days — starting from a single tweet. This behind-the-scenes look shows how ideas, production, and execution move at massive scale, all running in Slack. It’s a real-time example of how fast creator-led work can move when teams collaborate in one place. See how high-stakes campaigns come together under extreme timelines with @Slackhq and Slackbot.
